# Hero Section

## Overview
Full viewport height dark section. Two column layout —
content left (~60%), photo right (~35%). Vertically centered.
Dark background with subtle noise grain texture overlay.

## Accent Color
#CCFF00 — lime green. Used for primary button and highlight only.
Add to globals.css as --accent: #CCFF00

## Layout
- Full viewport: min-h-screen
- Two columns: content left, photo right
- Content: flex flex-col justify-center
- Outer padding: px-10 md:px-20
- Gap between columns: gap-16
- Section id: "intro"
- Position relative (for scroll indicator)

## Noise Texture
Add a subtle grain overlay using CSS:
```css
.hero-noise {
  position: relative;
}
.hero-noise::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,...");
  opacity: 0.05;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
}
```
All content inside hero must have position relative z-index 1
to appear above the noise overlay.

## Content — Left Column

### Label
`SAM DHANALAKOTA — SENIOR FULL-STACK ENGINEER`
- Font: Space Grotesk
- Size: 12px
- Weight: 500
- Uppercase, tracking-widest
- Color: var(--text-muted)
- Margin bottom: mb-6

### Headline
`Building AI-native products with TypeScript, React & Node.`
- Font: Playfair Display
- Size: text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl
- Weight: 700
- Color: var(--text-primary)
- Line height: leading-tight
- Margin bottom: mb-6
- Line breaks:
  Line 1: "Building AI-native"
  Line 2: "products with React"
  Line 3: "& Node."

### Sub Paragraph
`Full-stack engineer crafting secure, high-performance systems for enterprise teams — powered by AI.`
- Font: Inter
- Size: 16px
- Weight: 400
- Color: var(--text-secondary)
- Max width: max-w-md
- Line height: leading-relaxed
- Margin bottom: mb-10

### Buttons Row
Two buttons side by side, gap-4, flex-wrap

**Primary — VIEW WORK:**
- Background: #CCFF00
- Text color: #000000
- Font: Space Grotesk 13px bold uppercase tracking-widest
- Padding: px-8 py-4
- Border radius: rounded-full
- Hover: opacity-90
- On click: scrolls to #projects

**Secondary — GET IN TOUCH:**
- Background: transparent
- Border: 1.5px solid var(--text-primary)
- Text color: var(--text-primary)
- Font: Space Grotesk 13px bold uppercase tracking-widest
- Padding: px-8 py-4
- Border radius: rounded-full
- Hover: bg-[var(--text-primary)] text-[var(--bg-primary)]
- On click: scrolls to #contact
- Transition: all 200ms ease

## Photo — Right Column

### Container
- Rounded rectangle: rounded-2xl
- Border: 1px solid var(--border)
- Overflow hidden
- Max width: max-w-sm md:max-w-md
- Aspect ratio: aspect-[3/4]
- Position relative

### Image
- src: /hero-photo.jpg
- Use next/image
- fill prop
- object-fit: cover
- object-position: top center
- No filter — keep color

## Scroll Indicator
- Position: absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2
- Flex column items-center gap-2
- "SCROLL" text: Space Grotesk 10px uppercase tracking-widest var(--text-muted)
- Animated line below text:
  motion.div height 48px width 1px bg var(--text-muted)
  animate: scaleY 0→1→0 repeat infinite
  duration 1.5s ease-in-out
  origin-top

## Entrance Animations
Use framer-motion. All animate on mount (not scroll triggered).
Stagger children:
- Label: delay 0.1
- Headline: delay 0.3
- Sub paragraph: delay 0.5
- Buttons: delay 0.7
- Photo: delay 0.4, slides in from right (x: 40 → 0)

## Rules
- "use client" required
- Add Playfair Display to layout.tsx via next/font/google
- All colors via CSS variables except #CCFF00 and button black text
- next/image for photo
- No hardcoded layout values — use Tailwind classes
- Section id must be "intro"
- z-index 1 on all content (above noise overlay)
